# Build outputs
**/bin/
**/obj/

# IDE and editor files
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/*~

# Git
**/.git
**/.gitignore

# Docker files (to avoid copying into image)
**/Dockerfile*
**/docker-compose*
**/.dockerignore

# OS generated files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Logs and temporary files
**/*.log
**/*.tmp
**/logs/

# NuGet packages
**/packages/

# Test results
**/TestResults/
**/coverage/

# Node modules (if any)
**/node_modules/

# User-specific files
**/*.user
**/*.suo

# Build artifacts
**/artifacts/
**/publish/

# Environment files
**/.env
**/appsettings.Development.json

# Documentation and misc
**/README.md
**/HowToRun.txt
**/LICENSE
**/ArticlePlan/